    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT246-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">ciṟaippuṟam. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Hedge. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT246">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>peruṅkaṭaṟ karaiyatu ciṟuveṇ kākkai</l>
          <l>kaḷiṟṟuccevi yaṉṉa pācaṭai mayakkip</l>
          <l>paṉikkaḻi tuḻavum pāṉāṭ ṭaṉittōr</l>
          <l>tērvantu peyarnta teṉpa vataṟkoṇ</l>
          <l>ṭōru malaikku maṉṉai piṟarum</l>
          <l>piṉṉuviṭu katuppiṉ miṉṉiḻai makaḷi</l>
          <l>riḷaiyaru maṭavaru muḷarē</l>
          <l>yalaiyāt tāyaroṭu naṟpā lōrē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>A chariot came [and] went, they say,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">solitary, at midday, when the little white crow </l>
          <l rend="indent3">from the shore of the great sea disturbs the green leaves</l>
          <l rend="indent4">like elephant ears, [and] stirs the misty backwaters.</l>
          <l>There are young and inexperienced</l>
          <l>women with flashing jewels in braids coming loose </l>
          <l>– they [have] the better part, with mothers who don't slap [them] –</l>
          <l>and others with mothers who, taking that [as a cause],</l>
          <l rend="indent8">interrogate [and] slap [them]. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
